    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You spent <strong>6 YEARS</strong> of your life, perfecting the perfect science project. That is until an evil <strong>DEMONIC CORPO</strong> takes your project to <strong>DESTROY THE WORLD.</strong> With your trusty sword, <strong>ASCEND</strong> the corporate ladder and claim what is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060110/extras/c86c4c84f9c6cdd15e151b5c6c0c720a.poster.avif?t=1754067198\" width=550 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060110/extras/c86c4c84f9c6cdd15e151b5c6c0c720a.webm?t=1754067198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060110/extras/c86c4c84f9c6cdd15e151b5c6c0c720a.mp4?t=1754067198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Robo Rhythm</strong> is a stylish, pixelated rhythm game. As you ascend the neon-lit  corrupt corporation, <strong>FIGHT</strong> through waves of flying robots in six high-energy songs. Each pushing your reflexes and rhythm to the limit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060110/extras/dc7523a3fff6f071a10b7e3aa81a28b8.poster.avif?t=1754067198\" width=550 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060110/extras/dc7523a3fff6f071a10b7e3aa81a28b8.webm?t=1754067198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060110/extras/dc7523a3fff6f071a10b7e3aa81a28b8.mp4?t=1754067198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you reclaim your volcano and stop your deranged scientific rival, or will the rhythm get the better of you?</p>",
